<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Classic Slots | CashMash</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/slots.css"/>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %> 

<section class="slots-section">

  <div class="slot-header">
    <div class="neon-title">
      Classic Slots
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="user-panel">
    <div class="user-info">
      <span>ðŸ‘¤ <strong><%= user.username %></strong></span>
      <span>ðŸ’° Chips: <strong id="balance"><%= user.chips %></strong></span> 
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="slot-machine">
    <div class="reels" id="reels"></div>
        <div id="winMessage" class="win-message"></div>

    <div class="controls">
      <div class="bet-section">
        <input type="number" id="betAmount" placeholder="Bet chips" min="1" value="10"/>
        <button id="spinBtn" class="btn gold big">Spin</button>
      </div>

      <div class="info-icon" id="infoBtn">?</div>
    </div>

    <p id="result">Place your bet and spin!</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div id="infoModal" class="modal">
  <div class="modal-content">
    <span class="close-btn">&times;</span>
    <h2>Winning Info</h2>
    <p>Payouts require 5-of-a-kind on any of the 14 active paylines (horizontal, diagonal, and zig-zag).</p>

    <h3>Multipliers (5-of-a-Kind)</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><img src="/images/SlotsClassic/cherry.png" alt="Cherry" class="mini-symbol"/> Cherry: x1 (Returns bet)</li>
      <li><img src="/images/SlotsClassic/lemon.png" alt="Lemon" class="mini-symbol"/> Lemon: x1 (Returns bet)</li>
      <li><img src="/images/SlotsClassic/orange.png" alt="Orange" class="mini-symbol"/> Orange: x1.5</li>
      <li><img src="/images/SlotsClassic/watermelon.png" alt="Watermelon" class="mini-symbol"/> Watermelon: x2</li>
      <li><img src="/images/SlotsClassic/grapes.png" alt="Grapes" class="mini-symbol"/> Grapes: x4</li>
      <li><img src="/images/SlotsClassic/star.png" alt="Star" class="mini-symbol"/> Star: x5</li>
      <li><img src="/images/SlotsClassic/diamond.png" alt="Diamond" class="mini-symbol"/> Diamond: x8</li>
      <li><img src="/images/SlotsClassic/red7.png" alt="Red 7" class="mini-symbol"/> Red 7: x12</li>
      <li><img src="/images/SlotsClassic/bar.png" alt="Bar" class="mini-symbol"/> Bar: x20</li>
      <li><img src="/images/SlotsClassic/jackpot.png" alt="Jackpot" class="mini-symbol"/> Jackpot: x100 (Rare!)</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 15px;">**Note:** The high frequency of low-paying symbols contributes to a high "hit rate" while maintaining profitability.</p>
  </div>
</div>


<%- include('partials/footer') %>
<script type="module" src="/js/slots.js"></script>
<script type="module" src="/js/slotsModal.js"></script>
</body>
</html>